						<div class="postbody">Some of its features are probably not implemented in emulation. 7.5kB extra ram accessible via PPU address space, self modification (since it's flash), the two LEDs come to mind. I assume the LEDs were included as an easy way to say &quot;don't shut me off while i'm saving your precious game/modifying myself!&quot;</div>

					
