				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Many years ago, someone (tepples?) observed that &quot;XOR&quot; nametable layout (▞) should make almost-seamless scrolling possible ...<br /><br />We're pretty certain that no commercial games used it—preventing glitches just wasn't a high enough priority—but the hardware needed is trivial, and any mapper with the ability to arbitrarily configure nametables could be used to develop for it.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

